Feature list

Discussion

Specifications

Rate limits

The default is 180 requests per minute.

To increase your rate limits, contact support@1min.ai.

Credit limits

The total amount of credit available to the user within the team that owns the API key.

Check at https://app.1min.ai/members (required team admin role).

Create API Key

  • Register for an account on https://app.1min.ai/
  • Sign in and create an API key.
AI Feature API

A unified API endpoint for all AI services.

Endpoint

  • For streaming features (chat)

    https://api.1min.ai/api/features?isStreaming=true

  • For non-streaming features

    https://api.1min.ai/api/features

Request Header

FieldValue
API-KEY<api-key>
Content-Typeapplication/json

Request Payload

Please check for all parameters of promptObject
  • type feature name
  • model model name
  • promptObject all parameters of the feature
    • For streaming features (chat). Example:
      • Without context
      {
    "type": "CHAT_WITH_AI", // CHAT_WITH_AI, CHAT_WITH_IMAGE, CHAT_WITH_PDF (multi doc chat)
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "promptObject": {
        "prompt": "hi",
        "isMixed": false, // Mix models contex
        "imageList": ["img01","img02"], // when type is CHAT_WITH_IMAGE
        "webSearch": true, // true - false
		    "numOfSite": 1, // when webSearch is true
		    "maxWord": 500 // when webSearch is true
    }
}
      • With context (apply multi-ai chat)
      {
    "type": "CHAT_WITH_AI", // CHAT_WITH_AI, CHAT_WITH_IMAGE, CHAT_WITH_PDF (multi doc chat)
    "conversationId": "c5c5e1d4-76a9-46a6-bf6b-1ba843b838db", // From Conversation API
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "promptObject": {
        "prompt": "hi",
        "isMixed": false, // Mix models contex
        "imageList": ["img01","img02"], // when type is CHAT_WITH_IMAGE
        "webSearch": true, // true - false
		    "numOfSite": 1, // when webSearch is true
		    "maxWord": 500 // when webSearch is true
    },
    "metadata": {
        "messageGroup": "1727596968593_71" // Utilize random strings to categorize similar messages when interacting with multiple AIs.
    }
}
    • For non-streaming features. Example:
      {
    "type": "IMAGE_VARIATOR",
    "model": "midjourney",
    "promptObject": {
        "imageUrl": "development/images/2024_09_30_13_41_50_758_2023_11_10_16_27_12_416_208054.png", // Absolute URL OR "asset.key" of Asset API
        "mode": "fast",
        "n": 4,
        "isNiji6": false,
        "aspect_width": 1,
        "aspect_height": 1,
        "maintainModeration": true
    }
}

curl --location '<https://api.1min.ai/api/features>' \\
--header 'API-KEY: <api-key>' \\
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
--data '{
    "type": "SUMMARIZER",
    "model": "deepseek-chat",
    "conversationId": "SUMMARIZER",
    "promptObject": {
        "numberOfBullet": 5,
        "numberOfWord": 10,
        "tone": "informative",
        "prompt": "Tomatoes are nutrient-rich fruits composed mostly of water, making up about 95% of their weight."
    }
}'

Field Description

Field nameTypeSupported valueDescriptionRequired
typetextSUMMARIZERFeature name✔️
modeltextdeepseek-chatModel name✔️
conversationIdtextSUMMARIZERConversation ID✔️
promptObject.numberOfBulletnumber5Number of bullet points✔️
promptObject.numberOfWordnumber10Number of words per bullet✔️
promptObject.tonetextinformativeTone of summary✔️
promptObject.prompttextTomatoes are nutrient-rich fruits...Content to summarize✔️

Response Payload

{}

AI for Audio

Text to Speech API

Endpoint

https://api.1min.ai/api/features

Request Header

FieldValue
API-KEY<api-key>
Content-Typeapplication/json

Google TTS

Request Payload

curl --location '<https://api.1min.ai/api/features>' \\
--header 'API-KEY: <api-key>' \\
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
--data '{
    "type": "TEXT_TO_SPEECH",
    "model": "google-tts",
    "promptObject": {
        "audioEncoding": "MP3",
        "languageCode": "en-US",
        "name": "en-US-Casual-K",
        "pitch": 0,
        "speakingRate": 1,
        "text": "hello",
        "volumeGainDb": 0
    }
}'

Field Description

Field nameTypeSupported valueDescriptionRequired
typetextTEXT_TO_SPEECHFeature name✔️
modeltextgoogle-ttsModel name✔️
promptObject.audioEncodingtextMP3Audio file format✔️
promptObject.languageCodetexten-USLanguage and region code✔️
promptObject.nametexten-US-Casual-KVoice name✔️
promptObject.pitchnumber0Voice pitch adjustment✔️
promptObject.speakingRatenumber1Speaking speed✔️
promptObject.texttexthelloText to convert to speech✔️
promptObject.volumeGainDbnumber0Volume adjustment✔️

Response Payload

{}

ElevenLabs TTS

Request Payload

curl --location '<https://api.1min.ai/api/features>' \\
--header 'API-KEY: <api-key>' \\
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
--data '{
    "type": "TEXT_TO_SPEECH",
    "model": "elevenlabs-tts",
    "promptObject": {
        "apply_text_normalization": "auto",
        "language_code": "en",
        "model_id": "eleven_turbo_v2_5",
        "output_format": "mp3_44100_128",
        "text": "hello",
        "use_pvc_as_ivc": false,
        "voice_id": "9BWtsMINqrJLrRacOk9x",
        "voice_settings": {
            "stability": 0,
            "similarity_boost": 0,
            "style": 0,
            "use_speaker_boost": true
        }
    }
}'

Field Description

Field nameTypeSupported valueDescriptionRequired
typetextTEXT_TO_SPEECHFeature name✔️
modeltextelevenlabs-ttsModel name✔️

curl --location '<https://api.1min.ai/api/features>' \\
--header 'API-KEY: <api-key>' \\
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\
--data '{
    "type": "YOUTUBE_SUMMARIZER",
    "model": "deepseek-chat",
    "conversationId": "YOUTUBE_SUMMARIZER",
    "videoUrl": "<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GpNYaDkBcs>",
    "promptObject": {
        "videoUrl": "<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GpNYaDkBcs>",
        "language": "English"
    }
}'

Field Description

Field nameTypeSupported valueDescriptionRequired
typetextYOUTUBE_SUMMARIZERFeature name✔️
modeltextdeepseek-chatModel name✔️
conversationIdtextYOUTUBE_SUMMARIZERConversation ID✔️
videoUrltexthttps://www.youtube.com/...Full YouTube video URL✔️
promptObject.videoUrltexthttps://www.youtube.com/...YouTube video URL✔️
promptObject.languagetextEnglishLanguage for summary✔️

Response Payload

{}
